title: Ranked 3v3's not doing anything
body: my friend and i have played a good 20-25 games of ranked 3v3's the other night and yet my ranked placments are not going up? like they are not counting towards my ranked games.. i am quite confused.

replies.body: i was playing on this account. we had completed many ranked TT games and i havent seen my placement matches go up.
By your match history, you played 2 Normal (not ranked) TT games today, and 3 Ranked TT games 2 days ago. Beyond that it's pretty much all ARAMs, but there are no other TT games this season.
I can only see 3 ranked TT games in your recent match history, were you playing on a different account?
